description: Welcome to Zaan Homes—don’t miss one of the top units in this beautiful 65-unit community! This bright corner unit offers a spacious backyard, high-end finishes, and is move-in ready. Enjoy granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, laminate flooring, 9' main-floor ceilings, 2' blinds, and upgraded lighting throughout. Priced to sell & easy to show. Contact for your private viewing.
